Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.01,0:00:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a bus ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.26,0:00:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I bought it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.35,0:00:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.68,0:00:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,There are still ways to prove that you're innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.48,0:00:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.02,0:00:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not chasing after Johan to clear my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.78,0:00:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Rudy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.41,0:00:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma, you aren't going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.53,0:00:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right. I never looked down on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.71,0:00:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You looked like an interesting fellow,\Nbut I never had a chance to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.88,0:00:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But now we're finally friends, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.88,0:00:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw me cheat that time, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.72,0:00:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I was cheating, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.73,0:00:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.22,0:01:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see that sign just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.26,0:01:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No, sorry. I was dealing with this map.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.23,0:01:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it this way? Or maybe...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.56,0:01:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Which way do you hold it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.82,0:01:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you get that map?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.94,0:01:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be like that. I got it\Nwhen we got the rental car.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.57,0:01:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.08,0:01:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It must have been when I\Nwas in the men's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.71,0:01:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use. I can't read the\Nfine print on this map at my age.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.92,0:02:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have to deal with it since you forgot\Nyour reading glasses at the airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.80,0:02:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Wippenhausen, Ampertshausen, Gartelshausen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.09,0:02:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with those names? It sounds like you're\Nchewing on your tongue when you say them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.35,0:02:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,How interesting! I wonder if German people think\Nthe same thing when they hear English.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.31,0:02:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, what's the next intersection?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.15,0:02:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, there are some people.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.45,0:02:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's ask for directions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.66,0:02:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No, let's just keep on going.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.33,0:02:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But they're hitch-hikers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.25,0:02:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we give them a ride?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.42,0:02:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we going to do if we get into\Nsome kind of trouble because of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.92,0:02:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But look...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.34,0:02:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He's got that child with him, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.05,0:02:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel sorry for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.64,0:02:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we give them a ride?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.31,0:03:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great, isn't it, Tenma?\NThey stopped for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.36,0:03:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.92,0:04:39.13,Monster-Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(750,750)\pos(360,340)}Journey to Freiham
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.40,0:04:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Guten tag. Bitte...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.69,0:04:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't speak German.\NDo you speak English?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.49,0:04:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're English.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.74,0:04:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We want to go to Freiham.\NCould you give us a ride?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.45,0:04:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Give them the map.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.99,0:04:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.91,0:04:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.33,0:04:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the place you want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.37,0:05:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.66,0:05:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We're about here, so you'd\Nhave to go south for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.62,0:05:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the same direction we're going in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.25,0:05:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.96,0:05:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Danke-schoen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.83,0:05:21.16,Location,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)}Bayern State\N(Germany)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.05,0:05:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.77,0:05:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're definitely not father and son.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.48,0:05:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Asian, and he's German.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.73,0:05:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.57,0:05:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the child of a good friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.74,0:05:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Just from looking at you, I can tell\Nthat your some kind of specialist.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.83,0:05:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell by your speech and demeanor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.75,0:05:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey, please stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.13,0:05:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're being rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.67,0:05:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive him. He has some weird habits.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.13,0:06:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He used to be a policeman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.89,0:06:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What did they say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.43,0:06:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems he used to be with the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.56,0:06:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get off, Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.38,0:06:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.69,0:06:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So... your husband must be retired and enjoying\Nsome travel with his wife, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.11,0:06:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, he's always been a slave to his work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.54,0:06:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,When he was working, we couldn't even\Nthink of doing something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.62,0:06:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for bothering you when you're\Nfinally alone with your wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.88,0:06:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If we're in the way, we can leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.82,0:06:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.42,0:06:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since we got the rental car from the airport,\Nwe haven't been able to figure out the map.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.26,0:06:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't been able to\Norder food very well, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.93,0:06:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be much more confident if\Nwe had an interpreter with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.60,0:06:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.06,0:07:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do, Honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.19,0:07:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't do anything about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.03,0:07:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to go to the next gas station.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.95,0:07:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.70,0:07:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.33,0:07:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.35,0:07:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We're out of gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.13,0:08:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,In a place like this?\NI don't think I can help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.97,0:08:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I can only let two of you on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.01,0:08:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Jones.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.93,0:08:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. Just get on\Nand get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.56,0:08:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.85,0:08:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no reason for you to\Nstick around here with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.32,0:08:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,When I get to the next gas station,\NI'll tell them what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.99,0:08:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. We'd be grateful if you did that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.55,0:08:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That was pretty lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.43,0:08:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We found another ride so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.76,0:08:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.70,0:09:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Take us to the next gas station, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.87,0:09:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,There aren't any around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.02,0:09:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's getting late.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.23,0:09:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If he told them, the people at the gas station\Nwould come for us, wouldn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.03,0:09:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.20,0:09:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That man...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.41,0:09:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He might have just left us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.12,0:10:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey... No, he didn't. I thought\Nhe was a nice man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.63,0:10:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not so sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.85,0:10:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The sky is so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.98,0:10:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're talking about the sunset,\NI've already heard it many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.10,0:10:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already seen it many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.11,0:10:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not the sun setting.\NThe sun's already gone down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.20,0:10:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.20,0:10:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the color of the\Nsky after the sun has set.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.25,0:10:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Robert is also watching it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.00,0:10:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Watching this sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.84,0:10:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.21,0:10:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.34,0:10:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey, take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.89,0:11:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.69,0:11:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,See? I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.74,0:11:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew he'd come!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.12,0:11:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,A nearby farmer gave us\Nsome gasoline and a lamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.79,0:11:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,See, Honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.63,0:12:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.21,0:12:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think so, Honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.38,0:12:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.30,0:12:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to your translating the menu, we've\Nhad such a wonderful meal. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.89,0:12:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially that wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.69,0:12:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Forster Ungeheuer. It's wine\Nfrom the Pfalz area.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.65,0:12:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that "Leber" dish?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.07,0:12:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Leberknödel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.61,0:12:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it. It was really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.37,0:12:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If you weren't with us, we'd have probably passed\Nby the good German restaurants without noticing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.95,0:12:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No, thank you for treating us to a meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.08,0:13:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter, how would you like another ice cream?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.55,0:13:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No. He's had enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.76,0:13:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he's a criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.43,0:13:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm talking about the man I just\Nread about that killed his wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.23,0:13:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think.?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.23,0:13:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.07,0:13:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was a police officer, I had my\Nfair share of accomplishments.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.03,0:13:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.82,0:13:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell your old stories here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.16,0:13:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,When I looked at someone, I could always\Nfigure out if he was a criminal and whether\Nor not he was a bad person.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.05,0:13:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.80,0:13:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.01,0:13:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you drink too much wine?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.55,0:13:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet the longer I did it, the\Nworse I became at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.98,0:14:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Good people and bad people,\Nthe guilty and the innocent...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.02,0:14:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a sense for any of it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.74,0:14:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't that great a police officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.71,0:14:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I might have had too much wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.50,0:14:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you call this wine?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.38,0:14:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ungeheuer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.97,0:14:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It was good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.50,0:15:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,How cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.25,0:15:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it be nice if Dieter made a lot\Nof friends in a new place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.80,0:15:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.43,0:15:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone is happy during their childhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.93,0:15:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes me nostalgic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.81,0:15:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.40,0:15:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.78,0:15:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This should be the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.45,0:15:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.79,0:15:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go, Honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.00,0:15:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but we'll have to\Nask you to take a detour.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.00,0:16:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.68,0:16:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.94,0:16:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The police?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.62,0:16:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.08,0:16:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait in the car for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.13,0:16:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are we going to do, Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.27,0:16:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma, let's run.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.17,0:17:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.09,0:17:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like there's a car in the patrol car's parking\Nspace again. It looks like a foreigner.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.55,0:17:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.98,0:17:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.85,0:18:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, this seems to be the opposite direction\Nfrom Freiham, the place we want to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.32,0:18:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.15,0:18:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, this won't take much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.37,0:18:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I made some plans at Steinbach Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.62,0:18:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.25,0:18:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Steinbach Castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.04,0:18:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I want to see there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.61,0:19:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.19,0:19:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.42,0:19:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Our son wrote to us about this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.92,0:19:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He said that the view from\Nthis castle was wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.30,0:19:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He mentioned wanting to show it to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.18,0:19:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Your son lives here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.27,0:19:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We're on our way to see him,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.48,0:19:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,but we keep on making stops.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.79,0:20:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He was admiring this scenery.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.46,0:20:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Our son...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.42,0:20:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Our son killed someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.35,0:20:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We came here to see him, face to face.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.20,0:20:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be leaving now. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.70,0:20:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we thank you from the\Nbottom of our hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.96,0:20:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.30,0:20:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He was such a nice man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.30,0:20:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.43,0:21:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He's currently being pursued\Nas a murder suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.85,0:21:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That can't be. He...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.64,0:21:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.27,0:21:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw his wanted picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.98,0:21:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.32,0:21:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is that when I said "hello" to the officer who\Narrested Robert today, his picture was at the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.53,0:21:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.45,0:21:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a nice person?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.16,0:21:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.04,0:21:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Before I saw his picture, I doubted him,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.08,0:21:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and when I met him, I confirmed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.09,0:21:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He's innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.13,0:21:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He cannot be a bad person.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.47,0:21:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.64,0:21:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Our son, Robert, killed someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.85,0:21:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so ashamed that I couldn't even\Nface my friends and family.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.86,0:21:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,When I thought that, I quit the force.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.70,0:22:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to confirm one last thing\Nwith my own eyes, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.58,0:22:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Robert had committed a crime,\Nbut he's not a bad person.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.75,0:22:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Come...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.96,0:22:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go see Robert.
